reviewText:
This DVD has some great episodes on it including two of my favorite episodes. The characters all have a lot of entertaining challenges that they must overcome throughout the disc & it is fun getting to watch how they handle them as well as learning more about each character as the series progresses.

This DVD contains episodes 6 - 10
Episode 06.) Could it be Him? The Encounter Comes Without Notice
Episode 07.) Oh, Meow? The Demon World is Full of Cats
Episode 08.) Sparkle, the Me Within Myself
Episode 09.) Perfection? Enter the Princess of Heaven
Episode 10.) Is it Destiny? The Library Re-encounter
